%% Data Flow Diagram: Llama Stack K8s Operator
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / kubectl
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant Controller as Operator Controller<br/>8081/TCP HTTP
    participant Kustomize as Kustomize Renderer
    participant LlamaServer as Llama Stack Server<br/>8321/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,LlamaServer: Flow 1: LlamaStackDistribution Reconciliation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create/Update LlamaStackDistribution CR
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: Watch notification<br/>TLS 1.2+ / SA Token
    Controller->>Kustomize: Render manifests<br/>(base + plugins)
    Kustomize-->>Controller: Rendered resources
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create/Update resources<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP / SA Token
    Note right of Controller: Deployment, Service, PVC,<br/>SA, RoleBinding, NetworkPolicy,<br/>Ingress, HPA, PDB
    Controller->>LlamaServer: GET /v1/health<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP plaintext
    LlamaServer-->>Controller: Health status
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Update CR status<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP / SA Token

    Note over User,LlamaServer: Flow 2: Internal Client Access

    participant Client as Client Pod

    Client->>LlamaServer: POST /v1/*<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP plaintext<br/>(NetworkPolicy enforced)
    LlamaServer-->>Client: API Response

    Note over User,LlamaServer: Flow 3: External Client Access (via Ingress)

    participant ExtClient as External Client
    participant IngressCtrl as Ingress Controller<br/>80/TCP HTTP

    ExtClient->>IngressCtrl: HTTP Request<br/>80/TCP
    IngressCtrl->>LlamaServer: Forward to Service<br/>HTTP 8321/TCP plaintext
    LlamaServer-->>IngressCtrl: API Response
    IngressCtrl-->>ExtClient: HTTP Response

    Note over User,LlamaServer: Flow 4: CA Bundle Auto-Detection

    Controller->>K8sAPI: GET ConfigMap odh-trusted-ca-bundle<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP / SA Token
    K8sAPI-->>Controller: CA bundle data
    Controller->>K8sAPI: Create managed CA ConfigMap<br/>HTTPS 443/TCP / SA Token
